cqs: How many things could c1 do with something?
How many relations are proposed between c1 and something?
How many relations are available between c1 and something?
How many relations are described between c1 and something?
How many things can c1 do with something?
How many relations are there between c1 and something?
How many things may c1 do with something?

query: SELECT (COUNT(?x) AS ?cnt) WHERE { <c1> owl:equivalentClass [ owl:intersectionOf ( [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ; owl:onProperty ?x ; owl:someValuesFrom [ owl:intersectionOf rdf:nil ] ] ) ] . }
